    "Page 15 of 39 173",
    "Subsequently, we explored the application of sequential learning by progressively training an agent over multiple weather conditions, comparing its performance with that of an agent specialised in a single environment Finally, we compared the performance of the best DRL controllers of each building under different definitions of the reward function, mainly by varying the weights of the comfort and consumption terms and observing the results obtained.",
    "Both the training and evaluation of the DRL algorithms were executed using Google Cloud computing platform and Sinergym version https:// pypi.",
